column4: Acolytes of the Great Magnet of the Universe
Dammit now I want to try one of those Dorito Locos Tacos. I swear this whole Goss event must have been sponsored by Taco Bell.
The bottom is always soggy and breaks, but they are pretty tasty.
Double the calories and they cost the same?  That's value!
If youre thinking about calories but going to taco bell what the fuck are you doing
